Silhouette Score for each k value

In [28]:
silhouette_avg=[]
for i in range(2,16):
  #initialize kmeans cluster
  kmeans=KMeans(n_clusters=i)
  cluster_labels=kmeans.fit_predict(features)
  #Silhouette score
  silhouette_avg.append(silhouette_score(features,cluster_labels))
